</strong></span>Purchase Manager<br />
Apple Telesystems<br />
9th Street, Mahim<br />
Mumbai<br />
The Sales Manager<br />
Ganapati Stationery Mart<br />
Churchgate<br />
Mumbai<br />
12 March 20XX<br />
