Sir,<br />
We are a software company and we need the following items in bulk for office use. I request you to kindly quote your rates and terms of supply for the following items :<br />
<strong>1.</strong> Apsara Pencils - HB, HH<br />
<strong>2.</strong> Orient Bond paper - 25 dozen reams<br />
<strong>3.</strong> Cyclostyling paper - 30 dozen reams<br />
<strong>4.</strong> Computer paper - 20 dozen reams<br />
<strong>5.</strong> Type Paper - 50 dozen reams<br />
